---
title: Spicy Sweet Falafel Tacos with Sesame Slaw
description: Sweet, saucy and sticky, with just a hint of spice, these Asian-inspired sauced falafel tacos are incredibly flavourful. Topped with a creamy sesame and cucumber slaw, you might want to keep this one on high rotation!
